QUESTION :

Accept an integer N as the input. The program must print the sum of digits inÂ N as the output.

Example Input/Output:
Input:
12345

Output:
15

ANSWER :

#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>

int main()
{
int N, sum=0;
scanf("%d",&N);
while(N>0){
    sum+=N%10;
    N/=10;
}
printf("%d",sum);
return 0;
}
